You Are Booked!
===============================================

Congradulations!

You are now booked for the trip, "<%= @trip.name %>", at <%= @trip.start_datetime.strftime("%m/%d/%y %I:%M %P") %>.

If you have any questions for the driver, you can send a private message by using this link: <%= url_for new_message_path(:receiver => @trip.user.profile.id, :only_path => false) %>.
You will want to want to contact the driver to find out a pick up location, discuss compensation (gas money, snacks, etc), and any other question you
might have for the ride.

If you would like to send a message to the other riders in the trip, you can use this link: <%= url_for trip_path(@trip,  :only_path => false) %> and enter a comment.  You can also go
to the trip page (<%= url_for trip_path(@trip,  :only_path => false) %>) to view more information about the trip.

Thank you for using UrbanHitchhiker!
